<plot>Six days after the end of the Vietnam War, the crew of an American merchant marine vessel was taken hostage by the Khmer Rouge. Forty marines died attempting their rescue. Few know the real story. This film contains new never before seen footage and first hand stories combined in a documentary film for the first time.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?485091</url></doc>
